H=\left\{\begin{pmatrix}1 & b \\ 0 & 1\end{pmatrix} : b \in\mathbb{R}\right\}
G=\left\{\begin{pmatrix}a & b \\ 0 & d\end{pmatrix}: a, b, d \in\mathbb{R}, ad\ne0\right\}
